sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Authenticated user
    participant Card as Recommended-area card
    participant Modal as Consent modal
    participant Action as createLead /<br/>recordConsent action
    participant CR as consent_records
    participant L as leads
    participant E as Resend
    participant Inbox as kaz · craefto · admin@japanoma

    Note over U,Inbox: User has active consent already
    U->>Card: Express interest →
    Card->>Action: createLeadWithExistingConsent
    Action->>CR: SELECT active row (scope=lead)
    CR-->>Action: consent_record_id
    Action->>L: INSERT lead<br/>(area_slug · profile_snapshot · consent_id)
    Action->>E: notification email
    E->>Inbox: deliver
    Action-->>Card: { success, leadId }
    Card-->>U: "Interest recorded ✓"

    Note over U,Inbox: First-time interest (no active consent)
    U->>Card: Express interest →
    Card->>Modal: open
    Modal-->>U: show consent text + version + tickbox
    U->>Modal: agree + confirm
    Modal->>Action: recordConsentAndCreateLead
    Action->>CR: INSERT consent_record<br/>(version · hash · scope=lead · ip_hash · ua)
    CR-->>Action: consent_record_id
    Action->>L: INSERT lead with that id
    Action->>E: notification email
    E->>Inbox: deliver
    Action-->>Modal: { success, leadId }
    Modal-->>Card: "Interest recorded ✓"

    Note over U: Withdrawal — sets withdrawn_at on consent
    U->>Action: withdrawAllConsent
    Action->>CR: UPDATE withdrawn_at
    Action->>L: UPDATE leads SET withdrawn_at
